== Overview ==
The VR20 high-density "Hail Bringer" is the sister weapon of the "[[Storm Bringer]]" and is designed to annihilate unshielded enemies with a single salvo.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Hail Bringer can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Storm Technology]].
